::KitKat::

She looked at Megatron. "I was on my way to see a newly arrived bot 
when." her eyes widened. "Oh man, I forgot. I still have to go see 
them. Anyway, we were attacked by Allience troops as I was out to 
make a new ally for our team." She sighed and looked 
down. "Destructor," she said on him link," Please go and tell those 
new bots that I shall get there when I can."
